title: EU envoys OK more sanctions vs Russia
cleaned_sentences: BRUSSELS â€” European Union envoys have approved a new raft of sanctions against Russia, with the measures set to enter into force next week on the third anniversary of its full-scale invasion of Ukraine, a top EU official and diplomats confirmed on Wednesday.
